---
import DefaultLayout from '../layouts/DefaultLayout.astro'


---

<DefaultLayout title="Try our Laravel mail platform">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8 max-w-4xl">
      <header class="text-center mb-12">
          <h1 class="text-4xl mb-4">Introducing <b>Email & Call Center Platform</b> for Laravel applications</h1>
          <p class="text-xl italic">
              Built with love for businesses and developers.
          </p>
      </header>
  
      <div class="prose lg:prose-xl mx-auto">
          <div class="mb-10">
              <p class="lead">
                  This Valentine's Day, we're sharing our love for communication by introducing something that will make your heart skip a beat—Laravel Mail, 
                  a revolutionary self-hosted platform that combines email marketing with integrated call center capabilities, designed to help developers and businesses 
                  create deeper connections with their audiences.
              </p>
          </div>
  
          <section class="mb-12">
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">A Platform Created with Passion</h2>
              <p class="">
                  Born from the perfect match between <span class="font-semibold">SendPortal.io</span> and the sophisticated 
                  <span class="font-semibold">42workflows package</span>, Laravel Mail is now expanding its horizons with Asterisk integration. 
                  This isn't just <b>another platform</b>; it's a complete communication suite that brings email and voice together in perfect harmony.
              </p>
          </section>
  
          <section class="mb-12">
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Features That Will Make You Fall in Love</h2>
              <p class="mb-4">Discover an <b>all-in-one communication platform</b> that goes beyond expectations:</p>
              
              <div class="shadow-lg rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
                  <ul class="list-none space-y-4">
                      <li class="flex items-start">
                          <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-red-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                          </svg>
                          <span><strong>Complete Communication Control:</strong> Manage emails and calls from one unified platform, hosted on your infrastructure.</span>
                      </li>
                      <li class="flex items-start">
                          <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-red-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                          </svg>
                          <span><strong>New: Asterisk Integration:</strong> Set up and manage your call center directly through our intuitive interface.</span>
                      </li>
                      <li class="flex items-start">
                          <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-red-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                          </svg>
                          <span><strong>Cost-Effective Freedom:</strong> No more tiered pricing—own your communication infrastructure.</span>
                      </li>
                      <li class="flex items-start">
                          <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-red-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                          </svg>
                          <span><strong>Smart Technology Stack:</strong> Powered by Docker, enhanced by Reacher Email Validation, and now featuring Asterisk integration.</span>
                      </li>
                  </ul>
              </div>
          </section>
  
          <section class="mb-12">
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Try it Now</h2>
              <div class="p-6 rounded-lg">
                  <p class="font-semibold mb-4">Visit: <a href="https://app.laravelmail.com/login" class="text-red-600 hover:text-red-800">app.laravelmail.com</a></p>
                  <div class="p-4 rounded shadow-sm">
                      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Demo Access:</h3>
                      <p class="mb-1"><strong>Username:</strong> demo@demo.com </p>
                      <p><strong>Password:</strong> secret</p>
                  </div>
              </div>
          </section>
  
          <section class="mb-12">
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Communication Made with Love</h2>
              <p class="mb-6">
                  This Valentine's Day, we're not just launching features; we're creating connections. Our new Asterisk integration 
                  transforms Laravel Mail into a complete communication suite that brings email and voice together seamlessly.
              </p>
              <div class="bg-pink-50 border-l-4 border-pink-500 p-6 rounded">
                  <p class="italic text-gray-700">
                      Share the love this Valentine's Day with a platform that understands the art of communication. 
                      Experience the perfect blend of email marketing and call center capabilities.
                  </p>
                  <p class="mt-4 font-semibold text-gray-900">With love,<br>
                  <a href="https://laravelcompany.com" class="text-red-600 hover:text-red-800">Laravel Company Essex</a>
                  </p>
              </div>
          </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </DefaultLayout>
